{"tid":2516220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"落雨啦，但係我冇帶遮","createTime":"2021-05-04T13:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T13:28:26.000Z","uid":283704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd8e29e7fb4f96a6b6147710ca13402652cf5da","tid":2516220,"uid":283704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:27:28.000Z","msg":"我知冇帶係我抵死，濕身係自己攞嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，出個街買飯食啫，點估到會落狗屎啫。<br />\n<br />\n唔緊要啦反正冇幾耐就返去，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">你班撚樣有遮就咪鬼霸住啲遮雨位啦</span></span></strong>。我知你可能等車，但可唔可以收<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">埋把閪遮</span></strong></span>啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，條路好撚闊咩，知唔知口罩濕咗係玩緊水刑啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n有帶遮嗰啲，過人嗰<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">陣舉高少少</span></strong></span>得唔得啫，遮撞遮啲水會亂彈㗎嘛，有返少少禮儀啊。<br />\n<br />\n唔該你哋啊，雨季先啱啱開始，大家過得舒服啲啦好冇？"},{"pid":"f689031ef0df5eb087af22b5ad7eb34dae804198","tid":2516220,"uid":283704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:27:50.000Z","msg":"唔該你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7df6715e100d9d784dd7247404ed0ac34ed77a","tid":2516220,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"捉樓主執行水刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}